Author: CepheidVox
Text: This 100% sounds like an ED. Talk to a doctor, print this out if you have to and tell them everything. It's going to be okay, you just need to reach out to someone who can help you recover. Reaching out to a professional is really hard but it's worth it even if you're not ready to stop doing what you're doing just yet. Your physical health is very likely being impacted by this and a doctor can tell you how and what do to about it.
